# Registration Page Creation
- Registration onboarding system of LMS application should be based on REACT
- Registration page and intake wizard forms must be responsive
- Use bootstrap forms, group containers, and validation styles
- Form elements must temporarily cache step progress to session storage to avoid losing data on page refreshes
- Intelligently disable submit buttons immediately upon click to prevent double form submissions or duplicate transactions